## Stack framing notes (for proposal-writer)

The demo uses React 18 + Flask JWT. Frame for proposal:
- "The demo's role-based JWT auth (patient vs. admin) maps directly to Supabase Auth +
  Row Level Security policies in a Next.js App Router project."
- "The mock /checkout endpoint demonstrates the PaymentIntent flow; production uses
  Stripe.js + server-side PaymentIntents + Stripe webhooks for subscription management."
- "Vercel: Next.js deploys with Supabase and Stripe env vars set per environment,
  preview deployments on every PR, Edge Runtime for latency-sensitive routes."

